                makes available for professional
                <lb />or student the authentic interpre-
                <lb />tation of the world's foremost
                <lb />pianists.
                <lb />
                <seg ana="#analysis">
                    To study in close detail
                </seg>,
                <seg ana="#repeatability">
                    by fre-
                    <lb />quent repetition
                </seg>, the playing of
                <lb />the host of artists who record for
                <lb /><name type="brand">Welte-Mignon Licensee</name> is in itself
                <lb />a liberal education.
            </seg>
