            <lb />companists afford competent sup-
            <lb />port for singing at any time. On
            <lb />the stage, the ballets of the
            <lb />Chicago Opera and the San Carlo
            <lb />Opera have both given public in-
            <lb />terpretations of its sole accom-
            <lb />paniment.
            
